{First 2 letters of First word}{First 2 letters of Second word}
-
{First letter of 1st word of Brand}{First letter of 2nd word of Brand}
-
{First letter of 1st word of Item Group}{First letter of 2nd word of Item Group}
-
{Serial Number}


Examples

Item Name: Work Table, Brand: Acme Furniture, Group: Furniture → WOTA-AF-FUR-0001

Item Name: Office Chair, Brand: Good Home, Group: Seating → OFCH-GH-SEA-0001